            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (3)

- Shows update-check feedback immediately when Sparkle is still doing its installer-status preflight.
- Adds updater timing diagnostics to help spot any remaining delay between the user click, Sparkle callbacks, and result dialogs.
]]></description>
